e\"></i></div><button class=\"md:hidden text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] text-xl transition-colors\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><i class=\"fas fa-bars\"></i></button></div></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Cara Mengurangi Ukuran File Video untuk Email & Berbagi\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-10\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-10\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me\"},\"url\":\"https://toolpic.me/id/blog/reduce-video-file-size-for-email\",\"mainEntityOfPage\":\"https://toolpic.me/id/blog/reduce-video-file-size-for-email\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"ToolPic\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/id\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/id/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Cara Mengurangi Ukuran File Video untuk Email & Berbagi\",\"item\":\"https://toolpic.me/id/blog/reduce-video-file-size-for-email\"}]}</script><div class=\"background-grid\"></div><article class=\"max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-24\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300 mb-8\" href=\"/id/blog\"><i class=\"fas fa-arrow-left text-xs\"></i>Blog</a><header class=\"mb-12\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight mb-4 gradient-text\">Cara Mengurangi Ukuran File Video untuk Email &amp; Berbagi</h1><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-calendar-alt text-xs\"></i>10 Maret 2026</span><span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-text-muted)]\"></span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><i class=\"fas fa-clock text-xs\"></i>5 menit baca</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-12 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/blog/reduce-video-hero.jpg\" alt=\"Cara Mengurangi Ukuran File Video untuk Email &amp; Berbagi\" class=\"w-full h-auto\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-10\"><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Mengapa File Video Begitu Besar</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">File video besar karena berisi urutan gambar (frame) yang diputar pada 24 hingga 60 frame per detik, beserta data audio. Satu menit video 1080p tanpa kompresi pada 30 FPS memerlukan penyimpanan sekitar 10GB, itulah mengapa kompresi video sangat penting.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Memahami Resolusi dan Bitrate</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">Resolusi dan bitrate adalah dua pengungkit utama untuk mengontrol ukuran file video. Resolusi mengacu pada jumlah piksel di setiap frame. Resolusi umum termasuk 4K (3840x2160), 1080p (1920x1080), 720p (1280x720), dan 480p (854x480).</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Memilih Format yang Tepat</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">264 adalah format video yang paling kompatibel secara universal. Diputar di hampir setiap perangkat dan platform. Untuk berbagi via email atau pesan, MP4 harus menjadi pilihan default Anda.</div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[var(--color-text)]\">Kompresi Langkah-demi-Langkah dengan ToolPic</h2><div class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-[1.8] text-[1.05rem] whitespace-pre-line\">Buka alat Kompresor Video di ToolPic dan seret file video ke area unggah. Alat menerima MP4, WebM, AVI, MOV, dan format umum lainnya.</div></section></div><div class=\"mt-16 pt-10 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-wrench text-[var(--color-purple)]\"></i>Alat Terkait</h3><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><a class=\"glass-card p-5 block hover:border-[var(--color-border-hover)] transition-all duration-300 group\" href=\"/id/tools/kompres-video\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)]/10 to-[var(--color-blue)]/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-file-video text-sm text-[var(--color-text)]\"></i></div><h4 class=\"font-semibold group-hover:text-[var(--color-purple)] transition-colors\">Kompresor Video</h4></div><p class=\"text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Kompres file video dengan menyesuaikan resolusi dan bitrate.</p></a></div></div></article><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-[#040405] border-t border-[var(--color-border)] mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-10 mb-12\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-4\"><span class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-purple)] to-[var(--color-blue)] flex items-center justify-center\"><i class=\"fas fa-wand-magic-sparkles text-white text-base\"></i></span><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">ToolPic</span></div><p class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] max-w-[300px] leading-relaxed\">Alat online gratis untuk gambar dan video. 100% di browser, file Anda tidak pernah meninggalkan perangkat.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Alat</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/image-compressor\">Kompresor Gambar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/image-converter\">Konverter Gambar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/image-crop\">Potong &amp; Ubah Ukuran Gambar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/image-watermark\">Tambah Watermark</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/image-bg-remove\">Hapus Latar Belakang</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/video-compress\">Kompresor Video</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/video-convert\">Konverter Video</a></li><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/tools/video-to-gif\">Video ke GIF</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Resources</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><a class=\"text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\" href=\"/id/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4\">Hukum</h3><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li><span class=\"cursor-pointer text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\">Kebijakan Privasi</span></li><li><span class=\"cursor-pointer text-[var(--color-text-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors duration-300\">Ketentuan Layanan</span></li><li><span class=\"cur